<subsection xml:id="subsec-ratio">
    <title>Ratio</title>

    <introduction>
        <p>
            A ratio is a comparison of two numbers. 
            Ratios can be written in three ways: as a fraction, with a colon, or with the word "to."
        </p>
    </introduction>

    <subsubsection xml:id="subsubsec-Experessing-Fractions-as-Ratios-in-Real-Life-Situations">
        <title>Experessing Fractions as Ratios in Real-Life Situations</title>

        <activity>
            <p>
                <em><term>Work in Groups.</term></em>
            </p>
            <p>
                <ol>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            Divide a strip of paper into <m>8</m> equal parts.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            Color three parts red and five parts blue.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            Cut out the eight parts.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
